OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy in the north of the region with
OL,7,Fpatchy rain across the Peak District.
OL,8,FDrier in the south with a few more
OL,9,Fbreaks in the cloud. Breezy in places
OL,10,Fbut the wind gradually easing
OL,11,Fovernight. Relatively mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FGenerally cloudy for most with
OL,14,Fpossibly the odd spot of rain in the
OL,15,Fnorth. Some brighter spells developing
OL,16,Fin the south. Becoming warm as
OL,17,Ftemperatures increase in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
