OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA mix
OL,6,Fof cloudy periods and sunny spells.
OL,7,FOccasionally breezy, and becoming very
OL,8,Fwarm or hot in places as temperatures
OL,9,Fare likely to gradually increase.
